    EN: Restores a percentage of Max HP upon clearing a wave. \n {0}% HP Recovery
      on Wave Clear
  - Language_ID: 81522
    KR: "\uC2A4\uD14C\uC774\uC9C0 \uD074\uB9AC\uC5B4 \uBC0F \uAC8C\uC784 \uC815\uC0B0
